==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: băi huā qí fàng, băi jiā zhēng míng
===Etymology===
Literally: Let one hundred flowers bloom, let one hundred schools of thought contend.
===Phrase===
'''[[百]][[花]][[齐]][[放]]，[[百]][[家]][[争鸣]]'''
# This phrase was used by [[w:Mao Zedong|Mao Zedong]] in 1957 to launch the [[w:Hundred Flowers Campaign|Hundred Flowers Campaign]].

===Alternative forms===
